                                                                                                                                                  Deep Generative Models – Objective

                                                                                                                                                  q∗∈argminq∈Hd(pdata,q)

                                                                                                                                                   

                                                                                                                                                  Decoder objective

                                                                                                                                                  Objective (Decoder)

                                                                                                                                                  qθ(x)=𝔼ω∼pω[qθ(x|ω)]θ∗∈argminθ∈ΘdKL(qθ,pdata)

                                                                                                                                                  Formula (KL–divergence)

                                                                                                                                                  dKL(p,q)=𝔼x∼p[log⁡p(x)q(x)]

                                                                                                                                                   

                                                                                                                                                  Intractable objective

                                                                                                                                                  dKL(pdata ,qθ) = Ex∼pdata [log⁡pdata (x)qθ(x)]= −Ex∼pdata [log⁡Eω∼pω[qθ(x|ω)]⏟intractable]+constlog⁡Eω∼pω[qθ(x|ω)] ≥ Eω∼qψ(⋅|x)[log⁡qθ(x|ω)]⏟reconstruction−dKL(qψ(⋅|x),pω)⏟regularizerdKL(pdata ,qθ) ≤ Ex∼pdata [−Eω∼qψ(⋅|x)[log⁡qθ(x|ω)]+dKL(qψ(⋅|x),pω)]+ const 

                                                                                                                                                   

                                                                                                                                                   

                                                                                                                                                  Generative Adversarial Networks

                                                                                                                                                  • Distribution qθ∈Δ(Z)X

                                                                                                                                                    qθ(x)=𝔼ω∼pωδ[gθ(ω)−x]

                                                                                                                                                  • Objective

                                                                                                                                                    θ∗∈argminθdJS(pdata,qθ)

                                                                                                                                                  Formula (Jensen-Shannon divergence)

                                                                                                                                                  dJS(p,q)=12dKL(p,p+q2)+12dKL(q,p+q2)

                                                                                                                                                   

                                                                                                                                                  Equivalent form of the JS divergence

                                                                                                                                                  dJS(p,q)=12dKL(p,p+q2)+12dKL(q,p+q2)=12Ex∼p[log⁡p(x)p(x)+q(x)]+12Ex∼q[log⁡q(x)p(x)+q(x)]+log⁡(2)=log⁡(2)+12maxt{Ex∼p[log⁡t(x)]+Ex∼q[log⁡(1−t(x))]}
                                                                                                                                                  wheret(x)=p(x)p(x)+q(x)∧1−t(x)=q(x)p(x)+q(x)

                                                                                                                                                   

                                                                                                                                                  GAN objective

                                                                                                                                                  • Lower bound on the objective

                                                                                                                                                    dJS(pdata, qθ) = log⁡(2)+12maxt{Ex∼pdata[log⁡t(x)]+Ex∼qθ[log⁡(1−t(x))]}≥ log⁡(2)+12max{Ex∼pdata[log⁡tφ(x)]+Ex∼qθ[log⁡(1−tφ(x))]}

                                                                                                                                                  • Objective

                                                                                                                                                    Ex∼qθ[log⁡(1−tφ(x))] = Eω∼pω[log⁡(1−tφ(gθ(ω)))]θ∗∈ argminθmaxφ{Ex∼pdata[log⁡tφ(x)]⏟minimize classification error+ Eω∼pω[log⁡(1−tφ(gθ(ω)))]⏟minimize distinguishability}
